## 2. System Architecture (Contract View)

### Logical Layers

```
Electron UI (React)
  ↕ API Client (Typed)
Backend REST APIs
  ↕ Business Rule Engine
Persistence Layer
```

### Ownership Rules

| Concern                | Owner    |
| ---------------------- | -------- |
| UI state               | Frontend |
| Business rules         | Backend  |
| Financial calculations | Backend  |
| Ledger integrity       | Backend  |
| Navigation             | Frontend |
| Validation (final)     | Backend  |

Frontend **never** calculates money.

