## 11. Error Contract (Global)

### Error Response Format

```json
{
  "error_code": "PAYMENT_PROVIDER_FAILURE",
  "message": "Payment gateway timeout",
  "action_required": "retry_manual"
}
```

### Error Categories

| Code                    | Meaning         | UI Action  |
| ----------------------- | --------------- | ---------- |
| VALIDATION_ERROR        | Bad input       | Inline fix |
| AUTH_ERROR              | Session invalid | Logout     |
| BUSINESS_RULE_VIOLATION | Rule breach     | Block      |
| PROVIDER_FAILURE        | External        | Retry      |
| SYSTEM_ERROR            | Unknown         | Escalate   |

